snippet.title: Grime House Trailer
snippet.description:
Announcing Grime House an indie survival horror game in the style of the old Commodore 64 era of gaming.


Explore a rundown old house, defend yourself from zombies and worse. Escape the danger!


Buy Grime House here


https://skuttie.itch.io/grime-house
